title.rendered: HAN KJØBENHAVN AW24 during Copenhagen Fashion Week

content.rendered:
HAN KJBENHAVN Fall-Winter 2024 COLLECTION at Copenhagen Fashion Week

Founded in Copenhagen in 2008, Han Kjbenhavn is known for its distinctive design built upon uncompromising creativity, storytelling and craftsmanship. About The vision of Han Kjbenhavn is to create innovative designs that becomes emotionally inclusive to its audience. Based in Copenhagen and London, Han Kjbenhavn offers worldwide distribution of a full range of men's and women's ready-to-wear as well as accessories.

Runway Looks

Photo: Press Han Kjbenhavn

More on: @hankjobenhavn


By Senior Fashion Editor 24FashionTV: Christina V Henningstad @christina_henningstad
